DocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104dfn1665702688838.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dfn1665702688838.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dfn1665702688838.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"dfn1665702688838\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Is Modeled Component\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This property determines whether the component is a modeled component.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dfn1665702688838__section_w1100ab1b5b1_w1101ab1b5_w1102ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"dfn1665702688838__table_d10913e1_d10914e1_d10915e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dfn1665702688838__table_d10913e1_d10914e1_d10915e1__entry__1\"> Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dfn1665702688838__table_d10913e1_d10914e1_d10915e1__entry__2\"> Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dfn1665702688838__table_d10913e1_d10914e1_d10915e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dfn1665702688838__table_d10913e1_d10914e1_d10915e1__entry__2\"> The component is normal component or a derived\n                        component. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dfn1665702688838__table_d10913e1_d10914e1_d10915e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dfn1665702688838__table_d10913e1_d10914e1_d10915e1__entry__2\"> The component is a modeled component that can\n                        be used to create derived components that inherit component-level\n                        definitions from it. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dfn1665702688838__section_qfp_5zj_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d219325e109\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dfn1665702688838__p_d97367e1_d97368e1_d97369e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uhr1704434505611.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uhr1704434505611.html\" title=\"A modeled component is an abstract component definition that specifies a data structure, layout, and code for components that share a common purpose or similar behavior. It is used to create new components, known as derived components, which can inherit component-level changes made in the modeled component.\">Modeled Components</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dfn1665702688838__section_kyz_xzj_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d219325e128\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"dfn1665702688838__ul_pwl_zzj_4wb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dfn1665702688838__li_d39968e1_d39969e1_d39970e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ifc1665702608950.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ifc1665702608950.html\" title=\"A Component is a Main Development Object that defines an executable part of an application. It defines the data structure used to access data, the layout (if applicable) used to present it, and the actions used to modify, validate, and store data.\">Component</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612556\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612556\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Is Modeled Component Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Is Modeled Component This property determines whether the component is a modeled component. Value Description False The component is normal component or a derived component. True The component is a modeled component that can be used to create derived components that inherit component-level definitions from it. Description For more information, see Modeled Components . Applies To Component Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}